=== 評價 ===
電影贏得正面好評。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度高達88%，基於160條評論，平均分為7.1/10<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dont_breathe_2016/ |title=Don't Breathe (2016) |website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=2016-09-04 |archive-date=2016-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507035958/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dont_breathe_2016/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分71，評價良好<ref name="Meta">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/dont-breathe |title=Don't Breathe reviews |website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2016-08-25 |archive-date=2016-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160909085828/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/dont-breathe |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[互联网电影数据库|IMDb]]則獲得7.2/10的普遍好評。主要受影評人稱讚電影在有限的空間和簡單的劇情下呈現出的飽滿緊張感。根據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的評價在A+至F間平均落在「B+」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=https://m.cinemascore.com |title=CinemaScore |work=cinemascore.com |accessdate=2020-10-12 |archive-date=2019-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210223808/https://m.cinemascore.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

